  "description": "Echo rate at 38 Hz, resonance at 0.992 — the comb filter becomes a synthesis voice. At 38 Hz click rate, discrete pings merge into a sustained pitched metallic oscillator. The comb delay maps to note frequency, so the metallic tone tracks pitch. High echoMix makes echolocation the primary voice.",
